<title>USA: Burlington Industries to buy back 2 mln shrs.</title>
<headline>Burlington Industries to buy back 2 mln shrs.</headline>
<dateline>GREENSBORO, N.C. 1996-12-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Textile company Burlington Industries Inc said it would repurchase about two million shares of its common stock.</p>
<p>Purchases would be made in the open market or in privately negotiated transactions, the company said.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610.</p>
